high_descs: Turn around and go forward, and face the white table on the left.
Pick up the tomato at the front of the table.
Take the tomato and turn around. Go straight back, and turn left to locate the stove.
Place the tomato in the microwave and turn it on. Take out the tomato and shut the door.
Hold the tomato and turn around, then right to find the white table on the left.
Place the tomato on the table in the front.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and turn left to face the white, round table
Pick up the tomato that is sitting on the white table
Turn left and take a few steps then cross the room to the stove that is to the left
Open the microwave that is above the stove and place the tomato inside, then close the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the tomato then close the microwave
Turn around and cross the room, after you pass the counter take a right and walk to the wall, then turn left and face the round, white table
Place the tomato on the table to the left of the brown bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato on a table

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the white table.
Pick the tomato up from the white table.
Go left to cross the room and then turn left again to face the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave and turn it on and then off and take the tomato out and shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room and move to stand in front of the white table.
Put the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed tomato on a table.
